program define	 end_output_and_file, rclass
qui {
    syntax, handle(string) tempfilename(string) timestamp(string) [reportfolder(string)]

    local end_of_table "{col 4}{c BLC}{hline 60}"

    *Write the beginning of the table
    noi di "`end_of_table'"

